text: The Nepalese cricket team toured the Netherlands from 30 June to 3 July 2015 to play four Twenty20 International (T20I) matches. The Netherlands won the series 3–1. The tour was a warm-up for the 2015 ICC World Twenty20 Qualifier which took place in Ireland later in July. ==Squads== {| class="wikitable" style="text-align:center; width:35%; margin-left:25px" |- ! style="width:50%" | ! style="width:50%" | |- style="vertical-align:top" | * Peter Borren (c) * Wesley Barresi (vc) * Rahil Ahmed * Mudassar Bukhari * Ben Cooper * Ahsan Malik * Roelof van der Merwe * Stephan Myburgh * Max O'Dowd * Michael Rippon * Pieter Seelaar * Michael Swart * Timm van der Gugten * Paul van Meekeren * Thijs van Schelven * Tobias Visee | * Paras Khadka (c) * Gyanendra Malla (vc) * Pradeep Airee * Binod Bhandari * Shakti Gauchan * Karan KC * Sompal Kami * Avinash Karn * Subash Khakurel * Siddhant Lohani * Gyanendra Malla * Anil Mandal * Jitendra Mukhiya * Sagar Pun * Rajesh Pulami * Basanta Regmi * Sharad Vesawkar |} ==T20I series== ===1st T20I=== ===2nd T20I=== ===3rd T20I=== ===4th T20I=== ==References== ==External links== * Series home at ESPN Cricinfo Category:2015 in Dutch cricket Category:2015 in Nepalese cricket Category:International cricket competitions in 2015 Category:International cricket tours of the Netherlands
